# clasp pushes EVERYTHING under rootDir (".") by default — and this repo's root
# is full of files that must never reach Apps Script (worker.js, the whole
# public/ front-end, SampleData/, node_modules…). So: ignore everything, then
# explicitly allow ONLY the two files that belong in the Apps Script project.
#
# Touch this list with care. Anything you un-ignore here gets uploaded to the
# public web app on the next `npm run deploy:gas`.
**/**

!appsscript.json
!Code.gs
